snippet.title: Chaos Adventure Trailer
snippet.description:
New indie game coming in March 2024! Is there a back story? No... The adventure is yours to make! Pick a character, and you are dropped into the fantasy middle ages to start your journey! This game is designed for you to quickly jump right into it and begin hacking and slashing your way through! 

Check out the Steam store 👇
store.steampowered.com/app/2695400/Chaos_Adventure/
#gaming #indiegame #hackandslash
